
  Poliwag    Water Type Pokémon

  Its newly grown legs prevent 
  it from running.  It appears 
  to prefer swimming than trying 
  to stand. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Poliwag ► Poliwhirl ► Poliwrath

Stage 3 Forms:
  poliwrath
  politoed

